reviewText: This will teach me to buy something without reading the reviews. This is a waste of money.
NONE of the "Mastered in 4K" movies are presented in 4K.  They're 1080p.  If you want REAL 4K, good luck, there aren't any.
A HODGEPODGE OF POORLY SHOT IMAGES HARDLY WORTH WATCHING. EDITING IS TERRIBLE TOO. DEFINITELY NOT A GOOD SAMPLE OF 4K TV.
The pen drive is 12gb with 13 files containing mostly trailers... The worthwhile items being aquarium & fireplace of about 6min runtime
